BB10-Webworks-Packager Setup
----------------------------

1. Install node v0.6.10

2. git clone https://github.com/blackberry-webworks/BB10-Webworks-Packager.git

3. cd BB10-WebWorks-Packager

4. git checkout next

5. Run ./configure on Mac (sudo ./configure if you get permission errors) or configure.bat on Windows

6. Run 'jake test' and check that jake runs and completes

7. Try package the test WebWorks app in your development environment, run:

On Mac:
node lib/bbwp.js test/test.zip -o <output dir>

On Windows:
node lib\bbwp.js test\test.zip -o <output dir>